1. Open project in IntelliJ/Eclipse

2. Locate SpringSecurityApplication.java

3. Run as Java Application

# Method 3: Build JAR and Run

```
# Package the application
mvn clean package

# Run the JAR file
java -jar target/spring-security-project-1.0.0.jar
```


